text: The Angel of Mercy (, translit. Malak al-Rahma) is a 1946 Egyptian drama movie directed by Youssef Wahbi (who also stars) and also starring Faten Hamama, Farid Shawqi, Negma Ibrahim, Raqiya Ibrahim. ==Other websites== * Category:1946 drama movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies directed by Youssef Wahbi
title: The Angel of Mercy
